HEADWORD: Silverly
<hw>Sil"ver*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Like silver in appearance or
in sound.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Let me wipe off this honorable dew,⟦br⟧
That <qex>silverly</qex> doth progress on thy cheeks.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Silvern</ent>⟦br⟧
